{"tid":2396112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新蒲崗樂文文具腦細，被恐嚇「買起全家」","createTime":"2021-02-05T10:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T05:44:59.000Z","uid":387588,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"88a1b0703717126a45f1ae9edef4f47b8848161b","tid":2396112,"uid":387588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:34:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/103431747869822/posts/264753961737599/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F103431747869822%2Fposts%2F264753961737599%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjBTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=afbfe1f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/103431747869822/posts/264753961737599/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n罷【海寶食品超級市場】😡<br />\n自己唔好去買，屋企人買咗幫佢掉去垃圾桶🥱<br />\n<br />\n前排先同大家講去街市買嘢心得。其中有講過唔好幫襯啲阻街菜檔。啲間 ＃海寶食品超級市場 ，鳳凰邨新蒲崗都有分店。今朝 樂文文具公司  腦細欣賞食環署職員溫柔勸喻海寶唔好阻街時，慘被海寶警告要「買起佢全家」及叫職員跟蹤樂文腦細。真係CLS!<br />\n<br />\n其實啲間海寶已經日日阻街，又有呃人往績。多名本區區議員已經好努力要求食環署執法，但食環署嘅「懷柔政策」真係令人咋舌，結果阻街阻到出馬路，仲賺到開埋分店。屌那星💢！<br />\n<br />\n相片來源：樂文文具公司、新蒲崗互助網絡 - 陳啟淳、黃大仙區區友<br />\n<br />\n＃極少數叫人罷賣嘅post<br />\n#所以大家好好keep起佢<br />\n＃海寶食品超級市場<br />\n＃樂文文具公司<br />\n＃蒲崗互助網絡陳啟淳<br />\n#黃大仙黃色生活圈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MygiukN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMygiukN.png&h=6613e140&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6306d4772b4b14698adb14da509615fbd80ac10c","tid":2396112,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:44:06.000Z","msg":"海寶食品超級市場<br />\n<br />\n個名咁撚柒"},{"pid":"b2be4f856d796528df7fdd9b4abc85e0a40f6193","tid":2396112,"uid":34410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:46:42.000Z","msg":"幫佢入藍店list"},{"pid":"aa65b1156f7482caf62bc2838dac829e825191c2","tid":2396112,"uid":37525,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:54:03.000Z","msg":"呢間嘢個朵咁Q臭<br />\n又老翻pepe 又紙漫堂事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但仲賴喺黃圈做黃店<br />\n是非繼續多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a6347601cd46172aa6c424882a2f30818cfb2e","tid":2396112,"uid":53029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T11:08:41.000Z","msg":"咩位置？？大有街？？"},{"pid":"0ca55e89ff1a32e2ed7495190181f4747497117e","tid":2396112,"uid":358948,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T11:15:27.000Z","msg":"幫你改改標題<br />\n商舖阻街遭食環檢控，旁邊鶴湊熱鬧慘遭跟蹤恐嚇。<br />\n唔好博宣傳，ok?呢件事上面佢只係旁邊鶴，關佢係咩老闆果間係咪黃店咩事？<br />\n佢當左自己係名人？公眾人物？"},{"pid":"47838d1069eae70111fe0f633b3713a6a0e4406a","tid":2396112,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T11:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a8fef4c6b21a0ed9432bfeded0323650984ea3","tid":2396112,"uid":387588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ca55e89ff1a32e2ed7495190181f4747497117e","tid":2396112,"uid":358948,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T11:15:27.000Z","msg":"幫你改改標題<br />\n商舖阻街遭食環檢控，旁邊鶴湊熱鬧慘遭跟蹤恐嚇。<br />\n唔好博宣傳，ok?呢件事上面佢只係旁邊鶴，關佢係咩老闆果間係咪黃店咩事？<br />\n佢當左自己係名人？公眾人物？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T11:21:45.000Z","msg":"咁恐嚇你覺得ok?"},{"pid":"a85c6fada590c5820959973580615ef00f3662fd","tid":2396112,"uid":70629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T11:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmo